# Per-playthrough runtime state (not source)
# NOTE: the player-facing ui/ display files (ui/party.txt, ui/map.txt) are
# NOT ignored -- they are committed by `sheet` so the player reads the
# playthrough as blob pages on the branch (see dm.md). save.json and the
# developer-facing ui/fight.log stay runtime-only.
save.json

# Full combat debug workfile. Keep the old root path ignored too: builds
# before 2026-07-23 wrote there, and an existing local workfile may remain.
fight.log
ui/fight.log
